item.description:
Wanna catch a movie tonight with other members of the group? Woody Allen's latest movie, with Rachel McAdams and Owen Wilson (the blond Wilson brother), looks good. Here's the summary:

A family, including a young couple, travels to Paris, France for business and have their lives transformed.

The show starts at 6:50, so I suggest you meet at 6:15 or so in the ticket lobby to buy tickets.

This is a NoOrg, which means an organizer won't  necessarily be there.

Yes, this movie is TONIGHT, so RSVP now!

If you'd rather see this tomorrow sometime, please just comment on the meetup's page and self-organize that (like which show you'd like to see, when you'd like to meet, etc.).

Enjoy the show!

--Dana
item.how_to_find_us: Look for other members who have RSVPed
item.name: NoOrg: TONIGHT!! Midnight in Paris
